  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed first floor rear extension by reason of its inappropriate design, scale and   choice of finishing materials would form a discordant rear addition which would be readily visible from the public realm within this section of Riversdale Road. The proposed rear extension is considered to have a detrimental impact on the character and appearance of the host dwelling and its wider setting. The proposed development is therefore considered to be contrary to policies D1 (Overall design), D4 ( Urban context), D11 ( Alterations and extensions) of Islington’s Unitary Development Plan 2002, Islington’s Urban Design Guidance 2006."
